### Add a LICENSE File
1. Navigate to your repository by clicking the Repo tab on the left hand panel.
2. Click the grey **+ Add File** button.
3. Under the Apply a Template option, click the **Drop Down** arrow and select **LICENSE** > **GNU LESSER GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE**
4. Click **Commit Changes**.
5. **Check the Scanning Result**
6. Navigate to **CI/CD** in the left pane  Note the security scans are running successfully.
7. Click on **Security & Compliance** > **Configuration** and ensure that License Compliance has been successfully enabled.

